  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Oro Tendyris</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/50px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/75px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/100px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Oro Tendyris</b> is a merchant from <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oro_Tendyris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Bradamar_Frey\" title=\"Bradamar Frey\">Bradamar Frey</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Betharios_of_Braavos\" title=\"Betharios of Braavos\">Betharios of Braavos</a>, is Oro's ward.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The relation between Oro and Betharios is unknown, however.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Oro_Tendyris&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403203831\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.059 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.235 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 350/1000000\nPreprocessor 